
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 05 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Ligaments' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Medial collateral ligament tear' radio button is enabled
And 'Lateral collateral ligament tear' radio button is enabled
And 'Dislocation with lesions of MCL and LCL' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Dislocation with lesions of MCL and LCL' radio button
Then 'Stage 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage 3A' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage 3B' radio button is enabled
And 'Stage 3C' radio button is enabled
